#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.rfloordiv.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.rfloordiv"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_df_fill:1
#: of
msgid ""
"Get Integer division of dataframe and other, element-wise (binary "
"operator `rfloordiv`). Equivalent to ``//``, but with support to "
"substitute a fill_value for missing data in one of the inputs. With "
"reverse version, `floordiv`. Among flexible wrappers (`add`, `sub`, "
"`mul`, `div`, `mod`, `pow`) to arithmetic operators: `+`, `-`, `*`, `/`, "
"`//`, `%`, `**`."
msgstr ""
"获取 DataFrame 和 other 的整数除法，元素级别（二元运算符 `rfloordiv`）。"
"等价于 ``//``，但支持在其中一个输入中缺失数据时用 fill_value 替代。有反向"
"版本 `floordiv`。在算术运算符 `+`, `-`, `*`, `/`, `//`, `%`, `**` 上的"
"灵活封装包括：`add`, `sub`, `mul`, `div`, `mod`, `pow`。"

